<?php include "../header/header.php"; ?><html><body><div class="container"><br><h1>Text Formatting</h1><br><br>We can display text in different styles in HTML using these tags :<br><br>&ltstrong> - Important text (typically bold) :  <strong>Text</strong><br><br>&ltem> - Emphasized text (typically italic) : <em> Text</em> <br><br>&ltmark> - Marked text : <mark>Text</mark><br><br>&ltsmall> - Smaller text : <small>Text</small><br><br>&ltdel> - Deleted text :  <del>Text</del><br><br>&ltins> - Inserted text :  <ins>Text</ins><br><br>&ltsub> - Subscript text : T<sub>Text</sub><br><br>&ltsup> - Superscript text :  T<sup>Text</sup><br><br><b>Code Snippet : </b><br><br><code>&ltstrong> Bold Text</code><br><code>&ltem> Italic Text</code><br><code>&ltmark> Highlighted Text</code><br><code>&ltsmall> Small Text</code><br><code>&ltdel> Strike through</code><br><code>&ltins> Inserted Text</code><br><code>&ltsub> Subscript (for chemical compositions)</code><br><code>&ltsup> Superscript (for powers like square,cube etc.)</code><br><code></code></div></body></html><br><br><?php include "../footer/footer.php"; ?>